---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon';
---

<article class="px-2 flex-1 lg:w-1/3 m-4 flex flex-col gap-8">
  <img src="img/logo.png" alt="logo" class="w-64" />
  <p class="flex text-lg max-w-2xl text-gray-100">
    Ofrecemos sistemas de plataforma web, desde la cual usted podrá conocer la
    posición exacta y en tiempo real de sus unidades de transporte.
  </p>
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
    <h4 class="text-gray-50 font-bold">Plataformas:</h4>
    <a
      href="#"
      class="peer p-1 flex items-center w-64 border border-gray-300 cursor-pointer transition duration-300 hover:bg-gray-600"
    >
      <Icon name="world" width="50" class="stroke-emerald-50" />
      <span
        class="flex-1 flex justify-center items-center text-gray-100 font-semibold"
        >WEB</span
      >
    </a>
    <a
      href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.trebolcontrol.app"
      target="_blank"
      rel="external"
      class="p-1 flex items-center w-64 border border-gray-300 cursor-pointer transition duration-300 hover:bg-gray-600"
    >
      <Icon name="android" width="50" class="stroke-emerald-50" />
      <span
        class="flex-1 flex justify-center items-center text-center text-gray-100 font-semibold"
        >Descargar App Android</span
      >
    </a>
  </div>
</article>
